{
  "texts": [
    "In detail, we employ a conventional topic model, LDA (Blei et al 2003) and a neural topic model, NSTM (Zhao et al 2021c) to discover latent topics from real-world datasets.",
    "Then we ask human raters to evaluate the diversity among the top words of sampled topics.",
    "The adopted datasets are listed as follows: (i) NeurIPS, foot_5 including published papers at the NeurIPS conference from 1987 to 2017.",
    "(ii) ACL (Bird et al 2008), including research articles between 1973 and 2006 from the ACL Anthology.",
    "foot_6 (iii) NYT, foot_7 including news articles on the New York Times website from 2012 to 2022."
  ]
}